{"type": "article", "id": 30742, "title": "部落风格的镜子", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-08T23:00:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/201608081808169ikWnL560hUDN24t.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>你有没有好奇过自己穿上部落风格的服饰会是什么样子？<a href=\"http://www.teddy-moissant.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Teddy Moissant</a> 以传统的部落服饰为灵感设计了一组名为 Tribu marabout de ficelle 的镜子，为家具环境注入了一股自由奔放的气息。镜子的外围巧妙地利用了软木塞和流苏模拟出头饰的细节，这样人们就可以在这些五颜六色的镜子前看到自己更具有“狂野精神”的一面，兼具了装饰性与实用性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808182241IzpOeifGSXAaQqJ1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.117359\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608081822444h6gN1eKqfFWGR7S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808182243lo0RBFmVMAnugz7K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.528117\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808182244Plnx9pWqyzd5jLCt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.528117\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}